import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { 
  Typography, 
  Paper, 
  Box, 
  Grid, 
  Card, 
  CardContent, 
  Button,
  Fab
} from '@mui/material';
import AddIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Add';
import EventIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Event';
import PersonIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Person';
import ScheduleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Schedule';

const Dashboard = () => {
  const [bookings] = useState([
    {
      id: 1,
      title: '팀 미팅',
      date: '2024-01-15',
      time: '14:00 - 15:00',
      status: 'confirmed'
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      title: '고객 상담',
      date: '2024-01-16',
      time: '10:00 - 11:00',
      status: 'pending'
    }
  ]);

  return (
    <Box>
      <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
        대시보드
      </Typography>
      
      <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
        예약 현황을 확인하고 관리하세요
      </Typography>

      {/* 통계 카드 */}
      <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <EventIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'primary.main', mb: 1 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" component="div">
                {bookings.length}
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                전체 예약
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <ScheduleIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'success.main', mb: 1 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" component="div">
                {bookings.filter(b => b.status === 'confirmed').length}
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                확정된 예약
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <PersonIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'warning.main', mb: 1 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" component="div">
                {bookings.filter(b => b.status === 'pending').length}
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                대기 중인 예약
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <EventIcon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'info.main', mb: 1 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" component="div">
                0
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                오늘의 예약
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      {/* 예약 목록 */}
      <Paper sx={{ p: 3 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" component="h2" gutterBottom>
          최근 예약
        </Typography>
        
        {bookings.length === 0 ? (
          <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" align="center" sx={{ py: 4 }}>
            예약이 없습니다. 새로운 예약을 생성해보세요!
          </Typography>
        ) : (
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            {bookings.map((booking) => (
              <Grid item xs={12} key={booking.id}>
                <Card variant="outlined">
                  <CardContent>
                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                      <Box>
                        <Typography variant="h6" component="h3">
                          {booking.title}
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                          {booking.date} | {booking.time}
                        </Typography>
                      </Box>
                      <Box>
                        <Typography 
                          variant="body2" 
                          sx={{ 
                            color: booking.status === 'confirmed' ? 'success.main' : 'warning.main',
                            fontWeight: 'bold'
                          }}
                        >
                          {booking.status === 'confirmed' ? '확정' : '대기중'}
                        </Typography>
                      </Box>
                    </Box>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>
            ))}
          </Grid>
        )}
      </Paper>

      {/* 새 예약 생성 버튼 */}
      <Fab 
        color="primary" 
        aria-label="add booking"
        sx={{ position: 'fixed', bottom: 16, right: 16 }}
      >
        <AddIcon />
      </Fab>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
